thread.title: BRIEF-Carbon Black Inc Files For IPO Of Up To $100 Million

title: BRIEF-Carbon Black Inc Files For IPO Of Up To $100 Million
text:
April 9, 2018 / 3:50 PM / Updated 26 minutes ago BRIEF-Carbon Black Inc Files For IPO Of Up To $100 Million Reuters Staff 
April 9 (Reuters) - Carbon Black Inc: 
* CARBON BLACK INC FILES FOR IPO OF UP TO $100 MILLION – SEC FILING 
* CARBON BLACK INC SAYS IT INTENDS TO APPLY TO HAVE ITS COMMON STOCK LISTED ON NASDAQ GLOBAL SELECT MARKET UNDER THE SYMBOL “CBLK” 
* CARBON BLACK INC SAYS MORGAN STANLEY, J.P. MORGAN, KEYBANC CAPITAL MARKETS ARE AMONG UNDERWRITERS TO IPO 
* CARBON BLACK INC SAYS WILLIAM BLAIR, RAYMOND JAMES, COWEN ARE AMONG UNDERWRITERS TO IPO 
* CARBON BLACK INC SAYS PROPOSED IPO PRICE IS AN ESTIMATE SOLELY FOR CALCULATING SEC REGISTRATION FEE Source text : [ bit.ly/2uUNlHe ]
